  <acronym>CRYO-AF</acronym>
  <official_title>Cryoballoon Versus Irrigated Radiofrequency Ablation in Patients With Paroxysmal Atrial Fibrillation: A Multi-center, Prospective, Randomized, Controlled Study</official_title>
